WEBVTT

00:06.333 --> 00:08.291
[ SLOW-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

01:47.250 --> 01:48.792
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

01:48.792 --> 01:51.667
WHAT HAPPENED CHANGED
SOMETHING INSIDE YOU, DEX.

01:51.667 --> 01:53.750
IT GOT INTO YOU
TOO EARLY.

01:53.750 --> 01:56.542
I'M AFRAID YOUR URGE TO KILL
IS ONLY GONNA GET STRONGER.

01:58.041 --> 01:59.083
BEFORE HE KILLS
ANOTHER ONE OF MY GIRLS.

01:59.083 --> 02:00.542
WHAT CAN I DO TO HELP?

02:00.542 --> 02:01.834
Dexter: NO BLOOD.

02:01.834 --> 02:03.875
WHAT A BEAUTIFUL IDEA.

02:03.875 --> 02:05.333
REFRIGERATED TRUCK.

02:05.333 --> 02:07.792
HE WANTS
A COLD ENVIRONMENT

02:07.792 --> 02:09.875
TO SLOW THE FLOW OF BLOOD.

02:10.792 --> 02:14.834
I SUPPOSE I SHOULD BE UPSET,
EVEN FEEL VIOLATED,

02:14.834 --> 02:17.458
BUT I'M NOT.

02:17.458 --> 02:20.125
IN FACT, I THINK THIS IS
A FRIENDLY MESSAGE.

02:20.125 --> 02:22.917
KIND OF LIKE,
"HEY, WANT TO PLAY?"

02:22.917 --> 02:26.375
FINDING THAT TRUCK IS YOUR
GOLDEN TICKET INTO HOMICIDE.

02:26.375 --> 02:28.208
Debra:
So Miami's the haystack,

02:28.208 --> 02:29.625
and the ice truck's
the needle, right?

02:29.625 --> 02:33.291
I just found
the fucking needle.

02:33.291 --> 02:36.166
OH, THIS IS SERIOUSLY
FUCKED UP.

02:36.166 --> 02:37.792
I THINK HE'S TRYING
TO IMPRESS ME...

02:37.792 --> 02:40.583
AND IT'S WORKING.

02:40.583 --> 02:42.458
THAT CAPTAIN BELIEVES
YOU SHOULD BE REASSIGNED

02:42.458 --> 02:43.709
FROM VICE TO HOMICIDE.

02:43.709 --> 02:46.333
THANK YOU, SIR.

02:46.333 --> 02:49.667
RITA IS, IN HER OWN WAY,

02:49.667 --> 02:52.542
AS DAMAGED AS ME.

02:52.542 --> 02:55.166
ARRR!

02:55.166 --> 02:56.875
ARE YOU GONNA KISS HIM?

02:56.875 --> 02:58.500
ACTUALLY, YES.

02:59.667 --> 03:02.291
WE JUST GOT AN I.D. ON THE BODY
FROM UNDER THE CAUSEWAY.

03:02.291 --> 03:05.750
HIS NAME IS RICKY SIMMONS.
HE WAS A COP.

03:05.750 --> 03:08.166
Matthews: RICKY SIMMONS
WAS UNDER DEEP COVER

03:08.166 --> 03:09.834
IN CARLOS GUERRERO'S FAMILY?

03:09.834 --> 03:12.000
GUERRERO'S CROSSING
A WHOLE NEW LINE.

03:12.000 --> 03:13.583
NOW HE'S GONE AND PISSED OFF

03:13.583 --> 03:15.458
THE ENTIRE
MIAMI POLICE DEPARTMENT.

03:17.583 --> 03:20.375
IT'S ME.
IT'S JAMES, OKAY?

03:20.375 --> 03:22.333
IT'S OKAY.

03:22.333 --> 03:24.750
WAS KARA SLEEPING WITH SOMEONE
OTHER THAN RICKY?

03:24.750 --> 03:26.792
WAS IT YOU?

03:28.750 --> 03:30.208
JAMES, SHE DIED.

03:40.709 --> 03:42.834
[ FOGHORN BLOWS ]

03:42.834 --> 03:45.542
Mac:
MIAMI'S FULL OF GOOD COPS,

03:45.542 --> 03:47.750
A LOT OF THEM HERE TODAY.

03:47.750 --> 03:49.375
BUT NO OFFENSE --

03:49.375 --> 03:52.041
I WOULDN'T WANT ANY OF YOU
HITTING ON MY SISTER.

03:52.041 --> 03:54.667
RICKY WAS DIFFERENT.

03:54.667 --> 03:57.709
HE WAS THE KIND OF GUY YOU HOPED
YOUR SISTER WOULD FALL FOR.

03:57.709 --> 04:00.041
MOST PEOPLE HAVE A HARD TIME
DEALING WITH DEATH,

04:00.041 --> 04:01.792
BUT I'M NOT MOST PEOPLE.

04:01.792 --> 04:04.250
IT'S THE GRIEF
THAT MAKES ME UNCOMFORTABLE.

04:04.250 --> 04:06.834
NOT BECAUSE I'M A KILLER --
REALLY.

04:06.834 --> 04:08.959
I JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND
ALL THAT EMOTION,

04:08.959 --> 04:12.375
WHICH MAKES IT TOUGH TO FAKE.

04:12.375 --> 04:15.083
IN THOSE CASES,
SHADES COME IN HANDY.

04:15.083 --> 04:16.542
Doakes: MAC.

04:19.625 --> 04:20.750
I'M SORRY, MAN.

04:20.750 --> 04:21.917
THANKS, MAN.

04:21.917 --> 04:23.625
IT'S A FUCKING
TRAVESTY.

04:23.625 --> 04:25.375
YOU GOING AFTER
GUERRERO?

04:25.375 --> 04:27.208
GUERRERO ORDERED
THESE HITS.

04:27.208 --> 04:29.125
I'M GONNA MAKE
SOMETHING STICK

04:29.125 --> 04:31.000
TO THAT CARTEL
COCKSUCKER.

04:31.000 --> 04:33.041
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU AND RICKY WERE SO TIGHT.

04:33.041 --> 04:34.417
AIN'T ABOUT THAT.

04:34.417 --> 04:35.834
FUCK WITH A COP,

04:35.834 --> 04:37.959
YOU LOSE THE PRIVILEGE
TO WALK THE STREETS.

04:37.959 --> 04:39.583
YOU'RE RIGHT.

04:39.583 --> 04:41.542
...TRAGIC LOSS OF OUR
FELLOW OFFICER.

04:41.542 --> 04:44.083
BUT WE PRAISE HIS COURAGE.
RICKY KNEW NO FEAR.

04:44.083 --> 04:46.083
CAN YOU BELIEVE
LaGUERTA?

04:46.083 --> 04:47.917
SHE DIDN'T EVEN
KNOW SIMMONS.

04:47.917 --> 04:49.667
SHE KNEW HE WAS A COP.

04:49.667 --> 04:51.166
ER, WAIT.
DID YOU TELL HER?

04:51.166 --> 04:53.125
[ CHUCKLES SARCASTICALLY ]

04:53.125 --> 04:54.959
PROUD OF YOU FOR COMING, BRO.
I KNOW YOU HATE FUNERALS.

04:54.959 --> 04:57.250
HOW YOU HOLDING UP?
I'M MANAGING.

04:57.250 --> 04:58.583
NO, I'M NOT.

04:58.583 --> 05:00.458
KEEPING ONE'S FACE
PINCHED IN SORROW

05:00.458 --> 05:03.458
FOR TWO HOURS STRAIGHT
IS A REAL CHORE.

05:03.458 --> 05:06.834
A WHOLE LIFE REDUCED TO ASHES.

05:06.834 --> 05:09.875
FOR RICKY SIMMONS, IT'S OVER.

05:09.875 --> 05:13.667
BUT SOMETIMES,
YOU GET A SECOND CHANCE.

05:15.625 --> 05:18.875
FLORIDA PRISONS KICK FREE
25,000 INMATES A YEAR.

05:18.875 --> 05:21.500
THEY DON'T DO THAT FOR ME,
BUT IT SURE FEELS LIKE IT.

05:21.500 --> 05:25.041
I SEARCH FOR THE ONES WHO THINK
THEY'VE BEAT THE SYSTEM.

05:25.041 --> 05:29.875
THEY'RE NOT HARD TO FIND,
LIKE JEREMY DOWNS.

05:29.875 --> 05:31.583
JEREMY GOT OFF EASY --

05:31.583 --> 05:34.917
FOUR YEARS IN A JUVENILE
FACILITY FOR MANSLAUGHTER.

05:34.917 --> 05:36.417
TO THE CORONER,

05:36.417 --> 05:38.417
THE KNIFE STROKES
LOOKED RANDOM, IMPULSIVE,

05:38.417 --> 05:41.583
BUT I SAW THE WORK
OF A YOUNG VIRTUOSO.

05:41.583 --> 05:43.166
TOO MANY MAJOR ARTERIES
WERE SEVERED --

05:43.166 --> 05:45.417
FEMORAL, BRACHIAL, CAROTID.

05:45.417 --> 05:49.458
TODAY JEREMY IS JUST ANOTHER
PIECE OF TRASH ON THE STREET,

05:49.458 --> 05:52.000
BUT FOUR YEARS AGO,
HE WAS THE TOAST OF MIAMI.

05:52.000 --> 05:55.667
IT WAS A GRUESOME SCENE TODAY --
THE BLOODY BODY OF A TEENAGE BOY

05:55.667 --> 05:58.667
FOUND STABBED TO DEATH
INSIDE THIS SOUTH MIAMI PARK.

05:58.667 --> 06:01.792
POLICE HAVEN'T RELEASED THE NAME
OF THE VICTIM YET,

06:01.792 --> 06:05.041
BUT OUR SOURCES ARE TELLING US
THAT INVESTIGATORS ARE HOLDING

06:05.041 --> 06:06.917
A 15-YEAR-OLD SUSPECT
IN CUSTODY.

06:06.917 --> 06:09.875
WE'RE HEARING THAT THE SUSPECT
LURED THE OLDER BOY

06:09.875 --> 06:11.625
TO THE POND TO SPOT ALLIGATORS,

06:11.625 --> 06:13.375
BUT ONCE THEY WERE ALONE,

06:13.375 --> 06:15.166
THE VICTIM WAS ROBBED
AND REPEATEDLY STABBED.

06:15.166 --> 06:18.041
BUT I KNEW WHAT HE WAS
AND WHAT HE'D DO AGAIN.

06:18.041 --> 06:22.000
ALL I HAD TO DO WAS CIRCLE
MY CALENDAR AND WAIT.

06:24.875 --> 06:27.834
[ GRUNTING ]

06:27.834 --> 06:30.458
LEMONADE
FOR MY SWEATY WORKERS?

06:30.458 --> 06:32.917
WHAT DO YOU SAY, CREW?
ANYBODY PARCHED?

06:32.917 --> 06:36.041
WHAT'S PARCHED?

06:36.041 --> 06:38.709
WHEN WE PUT IN
THE NEW LEMON TREE,

06:38.709 --> 06:41.208
WE'LL BE ABLE TO MAKE OUR OWN
FRESH-SQUEEZED LEMONADE.

06:41.208 --> 06:43.709
CAN WE HAVE
A LEMONADE STAND?

06:43.709 --> 06:46.125
I'LL APPLY
FOR A BUSINESS LICENSE

06:46.125 --> 06:47.834
FIRST THING IN THE MORNING.

06:47.834 --> 06:49.834
THANK YOU FOR DOING THIS,
DEXTER.

06:49.834 --> 06:51.959
YOU KNOW, I MOVED HERE
FROM MICHIGAN

06:51.959 --> 06:54.208
WITH DREAMS OF FRUIT TREES
IN MY YARD.

06:54.208 --> 06:56.041
BUT THEY KEEP DYING.

06:56.041 --> 06:57.375
[ LAUGHS ]

06:57.375 --> 06:59.750
I CAN'T HELP IT.
I KILL THINGS.

06:59.750 --> 07:01.917
THAT MUST BE AWFUL.

07:01.917 --> 07:03.750
FORTUNATELY,
I HAVE A GREEN THUMB.

07:03.750 --> 07:05.834
THE KEY TO HAPPY CITRUS
IS A FERTILIZER.

07:05.834 --> 07:07.208
BONE MEAL WORKS THE BEST.

07:07.208 --> 07:09.291
Man: HEY, RITA.

07:11.792 --> 07:14.750
PAUL DOESN'T LIVE HERE
ANYMORE.

07:14.750 --> 07:17.458
[ CHUCKLES ]
NO SHIT. HE'S IN JAIL.

07:17.458 --> 07:20.834
BUT, UH, SEE, HE STILL OWES ME
FOR TWO OUNCES OF BLOW,

07:20.834 --> 07:22.750
WHICH MEANS YOU  OWE ME.

07:22.750 --> 07:24.333
DON'T GET INVOLVED.

07:24.333 --> 07:27.417
I NEVER KNOW
IN THESE SITUATIONS.

07:27.417 --> 07:28.917
I DON'T HAVE MONEY.

07:28.917 --> 07:30.125
YOU GOT A CAR.

07:30.125 --> 07:32.709
YOU WANT MY CAR?

07:32.709 --> 07:35.083
YEAH.
THE KEYS IN IT?

07:35.083 --> 07:37.250
YOU KNOW MY DAD?

07:37.250 --> 07:40.542
I SURE DO, LITTLE MAN.

07:40.542 --> 07:43.041
AND YOU WANT TO KNOW
SOMETHING?

07:43.041 --> 07:44.792
YOU LOOK JUST LIKE HIM.

07:44.792 --> 07:47.166
I'M GONNA TELL HIM
YOU SAID HI, OKAY?

07:49.583 --> 07:52.291
LOOK, IF YOU WANT,
I COULD GO IN THE HOUSE,

07:52.291 --> 07:54.792
THROW YOUR FURNITURE AROUND,
MAKE A REAL MESS,

07:54.792 --> 07:57.125
BUT WHAT KIND OF MESSAGE
WOULD THAT SEND

07:57.125 --> 07:58.834
TO THE LITTLE ONES?

07:58.834 --> 08:00.792
JUST GIVE ME
THE FUCKING CAR.

08:00.792 --> 08:02.917
WHY DON'T YOU GO INSIDE
AND GET THE KEYS?

08:02.917 --> 08:05.250
I'LL WAIT
WITH OUR FRIEND HERE.

08:07.166 --> 08:08.959
WHAT?

08:08.959 --> 08:13.291
YOU THINK YOU CAN TAKE ME
WITH YOUR LITTLE RED SHOVEL?

08:15.417 --> 08:17.583
[ KEYS JINGLE ]

08:30.834 --> 08:33.458
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

08:39.000 --> 08:41.458
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

08:44.583 --> 08:46.375
EVERYTHING OKAY IN THERE?

08:46.375 --> 08:48.208
Rita: [ SNIFFLING ]
YEAH.

08:51.125 --> 08:52.792
YOU NEED TOILET PAPER?

08:52.792 --> 08:54.375
NO.

09:00.166 --> 09:03.125
THE GUY CLEARLY HAD NO IDEA
WHO HE WAS DEALING WITH.

09:03.125 --> 09:05.542
I'LL FILE A REPORT AT WORK.
WE'LL GET YOUR CAR BACK.

09:05.542 --> 09:08.125
NO, UH, N-NO REPORTS,
DEXTER.

09:08.125 --> 09:12.041
THANK YOU, BUT, UH,
PAUL'S OUT OF MY LIFE.

09:12.041 --> 09:14.458
I FILED FOR DIVORCE.

09:14.458 --> 09:17.542
I JUST WANT MY PAST
TO GO AWAY.

09:17.542 --> 09:20.208
WELL, IT WENT AWAY
IN YOUR RAV 4.

09:23.041 --> 09:24.709
WHATEVER IT TAKES.

09:24.709 --> 09:27.792
I CAN GIVE YOU A RIDE TO WORK
UNTIL YOU GET ANOTHER CAR.

09:27.792 --> 09:30.959
OR I COULD TAKE THE BUS
LIKE MILLIONS OF OTHER PEOPLE.

09:30.959 --> 09:34.041
COME ON, LET'S GO OUTSIDE
AND ENJOY THIS BEAUTIFUL DAY.

09:34.041 --> 09:36.208
COME ON, KIDS.

09:36.208 --> 09:37.834
Angel: WHAT DID THEY USE,
AN AX?

09:40.083 --> 09:42.041
IT'S BLUNT FORCE.

09:42.041 --> 09:43.583
SEE THE WAY
THE HEAD'S CAVED IN?

09:43.583 --> 09:44.709
HMM.

09:44.709 --> 09:47.083
YOU GUYS CHECK OUT
THE NEW HOTTIE McGOTASS

09:47.083 --> 09:48.667
IN DISPATCH YET?

09:48.667 --> 09:50.291
SHE'S A BUTTER FACE.

09:50.291 --> 09:51.875
WHAT'S A BUTTER FACE?

09:51.875 --> 09:53.333
YOU KNOW, COMPADRE --

09:53.333 --> 09:56.083
SHE'S GOT A HOT BODY,
BUT HER FACE...

09:56.083 --> 09:59.041
HOW GREAT WOULD IT BE
TO PULL A BRONCO ON HER?

09:59.041 --> 10:00.959
YEAH.

10:00.959 --> 10:03.166
YEAH? MIRA A QUí.

10:03.166 --> 10:05.041
YOU DO IT DOGGY-STYLE,
RIGHT?

10:05.041 --> 10:07.250
AND JUST WHEN
SHE'S GETTING INTO IT,

10:07.250 --> 10:09.667
YOU GRAB HER BY THE HIPS AND YOU
YELL ANOTHER WOMAN'S NAME,

10:09.667 --> 10:12.083
AND BAM -- YOU'RE RIDING HER
LIKE A BRONCO

10:12.083 --> 10:14.250
'CAUSE SHE'S TRYING
TO BUCK YOU OFF.

10:14.250 --> 10:16.250
MANY TIMES IN LIFE,
I FEEL LIKE I'M MISSING

10:16.250 --> 10:18.083
SOME ESSENTIAL PIECE
OF THE HUMAN PUZZLE.

10:18.083 --> 10:19.500
THIS IS ONE OF THEM.

10:19.500 --> 10:21.375
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
OH, THE BRONCO.

10:21.375 --> 10:23.083
SEE, SOCIA?  SHE KNOWS.

10:23.083 --> 10:25.125
I JUST GOT MY FIRST
OFFICIAL HOMICIDE CALL.

10:25.125 --> 10:26.291
HE'S BACK.

10:26.291 --> 10:27.917
WHO'S BACK?
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER?

10:27.917 --> 10:29.291
THAT'S RIGHT.

10:29.291 --> 10:31.750
YOU WON'T BELIEVE
WHERE HE LEFT THE BODY.

10:57.000 --> 10:58.834
I KNEW WE'D BE BACK.

10:58.834 --> 11:01.750
FEELS LIKE CHRISTMAS MORNING.

11:01.750 --> 11:04.166
LOOK AT THAT --
A MIRACLE ON ICE.

11:04.166 --> 11:05.625
STUNNING.

11:08.166 --> 11:10.333
[ SIGHS ]

11:12.000 --> 11:14.709
YOU ALL RIGHT, DEXTER?

11:14.709 --> 11:17.000
THIS IS LIKE A DREAM.

11:18.500 --> 11:21.542
STANDING ON THE HOME ICE
OF THE MIAMI BLADES.

11:21.542 --> 11:23.667
I NEVER PEGGED YOU
FOR A HOCKEY FAN.

11:23.667 --> 11:26.333
YEAH, THERE'S SOMETHING ABOUT
STANDING IN A BIG, COOL HOLE

11:26.333 --> 11:28.959
I FIND VERY RELAXING.

11:31.417 --> 11:33.458
SO, WHAT DO WE KNOW?

11:33.458 --> 11:36.709
SAME AS THE OTHERS.
NO BLOOD.

11:36.709 --> 11:39.208
SO FAR, I DON'T SEE
ANY HESITATION CUTS.

11:39.208 --> 11:41.750
NO BONES FLAYED.

11:41.750 --> 11:43.583
I THINK OUR BOY'S
GOT HIS CONFIDENCE BACK.

11:43.583 --> 11:45.417
HE NEVER LOST IT.

11:45.417 --> 11:47.250
HE WAS JUST GETTING BORED.

11:47.250 --> 11:50.000
WHAT DO YOU THINK
HE'S TRYING TO TELL US?

11:50.000 --> 11:52.500
THAT HOCKEY'S
A VIOLENT SPORT.

11:54.583 --> 11:56.333
WHAT ELSE?

11:56.333 --> 11:59.125
HE'S ESCALATING THE THRILL.

11:59.125 --> 12:03.500
POSING HIS VICTIM IN THE MIDDLE
OF A 20,000-SEAT ARENA

12:03.500 --> 12:05.375
FOR ALL MIAMI TO SEE,

12:05.375 --> 12:07.333
TO SHOW THEM --
TO SHOW US --

12:07.333 --> 12:09.000
WHAT HE'S CAPABLE OF DOING.

12:12.417 --> 12:14.125
Debra: WHAT DID I MISS?

12:14.125 --> 12:16.709
Dexter: RELAX.
YOU DIDN'T MISS ANYTHING.

12:16.709 --> 12:20.458
YEAH, BUT SHE IS --
FINGERTIPS.

12:20.458 --> 12:22.208
THIS BODY BELONGS
TO THE FROZEN FINGERTIPS

12:22.208 --> 12:23.709
WE FOUND IN THE TRUCK.

12:23.709 --> 12:26.917
SHERRY TAYLOR.
IT'S ANOTHER PROSTITUTE.

12:26.917 --> 12:30.667
NO BLOOD --
NO NEED FOR ME.

12:32.125 --> 12:34.458
MORGAN, COME UP
TO THE COMMAND CENTER.

12:34.458 --> 12:35.875
WE MAY HAVE A SUSPECT.

12:39.583 --> 12:41.291
IS THERE REALLY A SUSPECT?

12:41.291 --> 12:43.083
I'LL LET YOU KNOW, BRO,

12:43.083 --> 12:44.875
WHEN I GET BACK FROM MY FIRST
OFFICIAL HOMICIDE INVESTIGA--

12:46.750 --> 12:48.917
I KNOW HER.

12:48.917 --> 12:50.583
SHERRY?

12:50.583 --> 12:52.959
YEAH, SHE CALLED
HERSELF CHERRY.

12:52.959 --> 12:56.125
UM, WE WORKED THE SAME CORNER
WHEN I WAS UNDERCOVER.

12:58.417 --> 13:02.083
YOU WERE, LIKE, FRIENDS?

13:02.083 --> 13:03.583
YES.

13:03.583 --> 13:05.417
DO YOU WANT A HUG?

13:05.417 --> 13:08.333
FUCK OFF.

13:08.333 --> 13:09.750
I TORE APART
THE SECURITY OFFICE.

13:09.750 --> 13:11.750
A SURVEILLANCE TAPE
IS MISSING.

13:11.750 --> 13:13.375
LET ME GUESS --
THE ONE COVERING THE ICE.

13:13.375 --> 13:15.709
THEY SAID YOU WERE GOOD.

13:15.709 --> 13:17.959
I'VE GOT THE PRESS KNOCKING
ON THE DOOR OUTSIDE.

13:17.959 --> 13:21.000
SOMEBODY WHO WAS HERE LAST NIGHT
SAW SOMETHING --

13:21.000 --> 13:23.166
RENT-A-BADGE,
UH, CLEANING CREW,

13:23.166 --> 13:25.166
CRACK WHORE
IN THE MEN'S ROOM?

13:25.166 --> 13:26.792
COME ON, WORK WITH ME.

13:26.792 --> 13:28.625
THEY GOT A NIGHT WATCHMAN,
BUT WE CAN'T FIND HIM.

13:28.625 --> 13:30.000
WELL, THEN, HE'S A SUSPECT.

13:30.000 --> 13:31.792
UNLESS THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER
ABDUCTED HIM

13:31.792 --> 13:33.542
TO GAIN ENTRY INTO THE ARENA.

13:33.542 --> 13:35.792
DID YOUR BROTHER HELP YOU OUT
WITH THAT LOGIC?

13:35.792 --> 13:37.542
THE NIGHT WATCHMAN
COULD'VE JUST BEEN

13:37.542 --> 13:39.458
AT THE WRONG PLACE
AT THE WRONG TIME.

13:39.458 --> 13:41.458
WE NEED TO GET TO HIS APARTMENT
TO SEE WHAT WE CAN FIND.

13:41.458 --> 13:43.041
I WAS HOPING
I COULD HIT KIOCHO,

13:43.041 --> 13:44.500
TALK TO MY OLD CONTACTS.

13:44.500 --> 13:46.375
I THOUGHT YOU WANTED
TO GET OUT OF VICE.

13:46.375 --> 13:48.583
ISN'T THAT WHAT YOU CRIED
TO THE CAPTAIN LAST WEEK?

13:48.583 --> 13:50.166
YEAH, I MEAN...

13:50.166 --> 13:51.500
I DIDN'T CRY.

13:51.500 --> 13:54.750
LISTEN, MY GIRLS
KNOW THIS VICTIM, OKAY?

13:54.750 --> 13:57.500
THEY MAY HAVE INFORMATION
THAT COULD HELP US.

13:57.500 --> 13:59.959
NO, I WANT YOU
TO WORK WITH DOAKES.

14:01.208 --> 14:03.625
MARIA, SHE HAS CONTACTS.

14:08.542 --> 14:10.792
YOU STILL GOT
YOUR TUBE TOP?

14:10.792 --> 14:12.792
AND MY NIPPLE CLAMPS.

14:12.792 --> 14:14.834
DON'T COME BACK
WITHOUT ANY INFORMATION.

14:33.792 --> 14:36.333
EVERYONE MOVES
TO MIAMI TO DIE,

14:36.333 --> 14:39.875
WHICH MEANS WE HAVE MORE JUNK
THAN ANY CITY IN AMERICA.

14:39.875 --> 14:42.834
A SKILLED BARGAIN HUNTER
CAN FIND REAL TREASURE HERE,

14:42.834 --> 14:47.041
BUT THAT'S NOT
MY IDEA OF HUNTING.

14:50.583 --> 14:52.917
I PREFER
A STALK-AND-AMBUSH APPROACH.

14:52.917 --> 14:55.583
MY INSTINCTS ARE IMPECCABLE,

14:55.583 --> 14:57.875
BUT I HAVE TO BE SURE
OF MY PREY.

14:57.875 --> 15:00.208
WE'RE ALL ADRENALINE RATS,
YOU KNOW?

15:00.208 --> 15:02.250
KILL IT TILL IT DIES.

15:02.250 --> 15:05.542
WE ALL MEAT HUNTERS,
JUST OUT LOOKING FOR DINNER.

15:05.542 --> 15:07.000
WHAT YOU LOOKING FOR?

15:09.333 --> 15:10.875
CAN I SEE THAT ONE?

15:10.875 --> 15:12.542
EH, GOOD EYE.

15:12.542 --> 15:14.542
IT'S A FIXED-BLADE
SKINNING KNIFE.

15:14.542 --> 15:16.166
FULL TANG, STAINLESS STEEL.

15:16.166 --> 15:18.125
REAL TIME-SAVER
FOR THE HUNTER

15:18.125 --> 15:20.625
WHO LIKES TO DO HIS OWN
BUTCHERING IN THE FIELD.

15:20.625 --> 15:22.834
SEE THE WAY THAT BLADE CURVES
LIKE THAT?

15:22.834 --> 15:25.667
IT'S LIKE
THE TALON OF AN EAGLE.

15:25.667 --> 15:28.792
15 BUCKS AND SHE'S YOURS.

15:28.792 --> 15:30.208
I'LL TAKE IT.

15:30.208 --> 15:32.583
HELL, YEAH, YOU'LL TAKE IT.
WHY WOULD YOU NOT?

15:32.583 --> 15:34.542
I'LL GET YOUR CHANGE.

15:44.417 --> 15:45.542
EASY, KID.

15:45.542 --> 15:47.542
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING, BOY?

15:47.542 --> 15:49.000
I DIDN'T SEE HIM.

15:49.000 --> 15:51.750
YOU ALL RIGHT, MISTER?
YEAH, I'M FINE.

15:51.750 --> 15:53.917
HONEST MISTAKE.
NO HARM.

15:53.917 --> 15:55.667
HEY.

15:55.667 --> 15:58.041
YOU BE CAREFUL
WITH THAT THING, HUH?

16:02.375 --> 16:04.542
SORRY ABOUT THAT, BOSS.

16:04.542 --> 16:06.000
I ONLY SELL THEM.

16:06.000 --> 16:07.500
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:07.500 --> 16:09.917
SO, WHAT YOU HUNT --
TROPHIES OR MEAT?

16:14.458 --> 16:17.583
WHAT DO YOU THINK TODAY, DEX?
THE WINCHESTER?

16:18.792 --> 16:20.417
WHAT ABOUT THE 9mm?

16:20.417 --> 16:22.125
A HANDGUN?

16:22.125 --> 16:24.750
NOT EXACTLY THE WEAPON OF CHOICE
FOR PHEASANTS.

16:24.750 --> 16:26.458
YOU NEED A WIDE SPREAD
TO BRING THEM DOWN.

16:31.959 --> 16:34.291
DID YOU EVER
SHOOT ANYBODY, DAD?

16:34.291 --> 16:36.500
AFRAID SO.

16:36.500 --> 16:38.917
ANY OF THEM DIE?

16:38.917 --> 16:40.959
JUST ONE.

16:40.959 --> 16:45.667
HOW'D IT FEEL...
TO KILL A GUY?

16:45.667 --> 16:48.125
NOT SO GREAT, DEX.

16:54.333 --> 16:56.667
WHEN YOU TAKE A MAN'S LIFE,
YOU'RE NOT JUST KILLING THEM.

16:56.667 --> 16:59.625
YOU'RE SNUFFING OUT ALL
THE THINGS HE'LL EVER BECOME.

17:03.083 --> 17:05.542
AS A COP, I ONLY FIRE MY WEAPON
TO SAVE A LIFE.

17:05.542 --> 17:07.792
THAT'S A CODE I LIVE BY.

17:07.792 --> 17:09.834
KILLING MUST SERVE
A PURPOSE.

17:09.834 --> 17:12.208
OTHERWISE,
IT'S JUST PLAIN MURDER.

17:12.208 --> 17:15.917
YOU UNDERSTAND?

17:15.917 --> 17:17.125
YEAH.

17:20.375 --> 17:21.792
CHANGED MY MIND.

17:26.333 --> 17:28.250
I THINK
WE'LL TAKE THE RUGER.

17:30.458 --> 17:31.542
RIFLE?

17:31.542 --> 17:33.792
I THOUGHT THAT SHOTGUNS
WERE BEST FOR PHEASANTS.

17:33.792 --> 17:35.583
WE'RE NOT GONNA
HUNT PHEASANTS.

17:36.959 --> 17:38.583
[ GUNSHOT ]

17:41.667 --> 17:43.041
IT'S A BIG ONE.

17:43.041 --> 17:45.083
[ Laughing ] YEAH.

17:48.542 --> 17:51.542
THIS DEER WILL PUT MEAT
ON OUR TABLE TONIGHT.

17:51.542 --> 17:53.583
IT'S STILL ALIVE.

18:00.917 --> 18:04.125
FOR NOW, THIS HUNT WILL CONTROL
THE URGES YOU FEEL.

18:04.125 --> 18:05.959
CHANNEL THEM.

18:05.959 --> 18:08.083
WHY DON'T YOU
GO AHEAD, SON?

18:08.083 --> 18:09.959
REALLY?

18:19.417 --> 18:22.208
PUT THE POOR ANIMAL
OUT OF ITS MISERY.

18:45.792 --> 18:48.250
[ SPANISH MUSIC PLAYS ]

18:50.625 --> 18:52.250
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

19:19.542 --> 19:21.250
VODKA, PLEASE.

19:27.500 --> 19:28.834
HI, ROSE.

19:28.834 --> 19:30.166
HI.

19:30.166 --> 19:32.000
CONGRATULATIONS
ON YOUR CONFIRMATION.

19:32.000 --> 19:34.083
THANK YOU.
DO I KNOW YOU?

19:34.083 --> 19:36.625
MY NAME'S JAMES DOAKES.
MIAMI METRO P.D.

19:36.625 --> 19:38.959
I'M INVESTIGATING
THE MURDER

19:38.959 --> 19:41.291
OF AN UNDERCOVER COP
AND HIS WIFE.

19:41.291 --> 19:43.000
OH, THAT'S TERRIBLE.

19:43.000 --> 19:45.291
WERE THEY MEMBERS
OF THE CHURCH?

19:45.291 --> 19:47.166
NO, ROSE, THEY WEREN'T.

19:47.166 --> 19:49.208
OH, I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

19:49.208 --> 19:52.166
ROSE, HAVE YOU EVER
SEEN THIS MAN BEFORE?

19:52.166 --> 19:54.917
I DON'T KNOW.
WHY ARE YOU ASKING ME?

19:54.917 --> 19:57.291
GET AWAY
FROM MY DAUGHTER.

19:57.291 --> 20:00.709
IT'S OKAY.

20:00.709 --> 20:02.333
AT MY CHURCH?

20:02.333 --> 20:04.625
IN FRONT OF MY FAMILY?

20:04.625 --> 20:07.000
RICKY AND KARA
HAD A FAMILY, TOO.

20:09.792 --> 20:12.917
YOU JUST OPENED
A DANGEROUS DOOR.

20:12.917 --> 20:14.291
NO, MAN, YOU DID...

20:14.291 --> 20:17.834
WHEN YOU MURDERED A COP
AND AN INNOCENT LADY.

20:17.834 --> 20:20.166
WHAT IS HE
TALKING ABOUT, DADDY?

20:20.166 --> 20:22.333
Woman: COME ON, HONEY.
LET'S GO.

20:22.333 --> 20:23.500
LET'S GO!

20:23.500 --> 20:25.417
YOU DON'T PLAY
BY THE RULES, GUERRERO.

20:25.417 --> 20:26.542
WHY SHOULD I?

20:38.208 --> 20:41.333
Woman: YOU'VE GOT FIVE MINUTES,
BIZACH, OKAY?

20:43.917 --> 20:46.041
YO, LOOK WHO'S BACK.

20:46.041 --> 20:49.417
PERO MIRELA,
COMO ESTá CALIENTE!

20:52.333 --> 20:54.166
WHO'D YOU FUCK --
DOLCE OR GABBANA?

20:54.166 --> 20:56.500
I LET THEM BOTH
PULL A TRAIN, OKAY?

20:56.500 --> 20:59.375
LISTEN, I, UH, I GOT
A CONFESSION TO MAKE.

20:59.375 --> 21:02.458
I'M, UH...
I'M NOT WHO YOU THINK I AM.

21:02.458 --> 21:04.583
I'M A COP.

21:04.583 --> 21:06.125
BRIDGETT, GET BACK --
BRIDGETT!

21:06.125 --> 21:07.583
I'M NOT GONNA BUST --

21:07.583 --> 21:09.166
YOU'RE NOT A COP.
YOU'RE A WHORE.

21:09.166 --> 21:10.792
I'M NOT A FUCKING WHORE.

21:10.792 --> 21:12.291
WHAT'S WRONG WITH BEING
A FUCKING WHORE, HUH?

21:12.291 --> 21:14.083
WE TRUSTED YOU, BRANDY.

21:14.083 --> 21:16.208
MY NAME'S DEBRA, OKAY?
AND I'M NOT HERE TO BUST YOU.

21:16.208 --> 21:18.250
HE HIT AGAIN --
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

21:18.250 --> 21:19.750
HE GOT CHERRY.

21:19.750 --> 21:21.458
CHERRY?

21:21.458 --> 21:23.291
[ SIGHS ]

21:26.709 --> 21:29.083
Woman: THIS SHIT'S CRAZY.
I'M OUT.

21:29.083 --> 21:31.166
I GOT A SISTER
WHO LIVES IN OHIO,

21:31.166 --> 21:33.291
RUNS A FASHION-BOUTIQUE
STORE.

21:33.291 --> 21:34.959
I'M ON THE BUS TOMORROW.

21:34.959 --> 21:37.917
I AIN'T CLOSING MY SHOP
FOR NO SICK, PSYCHO BITCH.

21:37.917 --> 21:39.875
FUCKING WOMAN-HATER.

21:39.875 --> 21:42.959
I WAS ON THE STREET BEFORE HIM.
FUCK IT.

21:42.959 --> 21:44.250
I CAN GET HIM, YOU GUYS.

21:44.250 --> 21:46.375
YOU JUST GOT
TO GIVE ME SOMETHING.

21:46.375 --> 21:48.083
DID ANY OF YOU ALL
SEE CHERRY WITH ANYONE

21:48.083 --> 21:49.709
THE NIGHT BEFORE LAST?

21:49.709 --> 21:52.166
WELL, I SAW HER
LAST NIGHT,

21:52.166 --> 21:54.333
AND THEN SHE GOT INTO A CAR
AND NEVER CAME BACK.

21:54.333 --> 21:56.208
BUT I WAS WORKING
ALL NIGHT, SO...

21:56.208 --> 21:57.959
YOU KNOW THE DRIVER?

21:57.959 --> 22:01.458
NO, BUT THE CAR WAS, LIKE,
ONE OF THOSE OLD STATION WAGONS

22:01.458 --> 22:03.375
THAT HAVE, LIKE,
WOOD PANELS ON THE SIDE.

22:03.375 --> 22:06.625
THIS IS GOOD. THIS IS GOOD.
THIS IS A LEAD.

22:06.625 --> 22:09.500
I SHOULD GO GET LaGUERTA
TO LISTEN.

22:09.500 --> 22:10.792
WHO'S LaGUERTA?

22:10.792 --> 22:12.500
UH, SHE'S MY LIEUTENANT.
SHE HATES ME.

22:12.500 --> 22:14.667
BUT I'M CLOSE WITH THE CAPTAIN.
I'LL TALK TO HIM.

22:14.667 --> 22:16.208
[ WHISTLES ]

22:16.208 --> 22:17.917
WHAT?

22:17.917 --> 22:19.709
NEVER PISS OFF YOUR PIMP.

22:19.709 --> 22:22.208
LaGUERTA'S NOT MY PIMP.

22:22.208 --> 22:23.834
IS THAT RIGHT?

22:23.834 --> 22:25.333
BITCH TELL YOU
WHAT TO DO?

22:25.333 --> 22:27.291
Woman: IS YOUR PUSSY
TAKING ALL THE GRIEF?

22:27.291 --> 22:29.125
DOES SHE STEAL
EVERYTHING YOU EARN?

22:29.125 --> 22:31.417
YEAH, SHE DEFINITELY
DOES THAT.

22:31.417 --> 22:33.500
THEN SHE'S YOUR PIMP, BABY,

22:33.500 --> 22:37.417
AND SHE WILL MESS YOU UP
IF YOU PLAY HER.

22:37.417 --> 22:39.166
I TOLD YOU --
I'M NOT A FUCKING WHORE.

22:39.166 --> 22:41.291
WHAT'S WRONG WITH BEING
A FUCKING WHORE?

22:48.041 --> 22:49.333
HEY.

22:49.333 --> 22:50.792
BOUGHT YOU A PRESENT

22:50.792 --> 22:54.875
TO CELEBRATE YOUR FIRST
OFFICIAL HOMICIDE CASE.

22:54.875 --> 22:56.875
SERIOUSLY?

22:56.875 --> 23:00.000
[ GASPS ]
IT'S A CACTUS.

23:00.000 --> 23:02.542
YOU ONLY HAVE TO WATER IT
THREE TIMES A YEAR.

23:02.542 --> 23:05.583
GEE, DEX, YOU DIDN'T
HAVE TO GO OUT OF YOUR WAY.

23:05.583 --> 23:07.542
I DIDN'T.
I WAS AT THE SWAP MEET.

23:09.208 --> 23:12.125
SO, ANY NEWS
ON OUR FROSTY FRIEND?

23:12.125 --> 23:14.208
ONE OF MY CONTACTS
SAID SHE SAW CHERRY

23:14.208 --> 23:16.166
GETTING IN A WOOD-PANEL
STATION WAGON

23:16.166 --> 23:17.542
THE NIGHT SHE DIED.

23:17.542 --> 23:19.500
DID YOU CHECK
THE DMV DATABASE?

23:19.500 --> 23:21.166
AS WE SPEAK.

23:21.166 --> 23:23.709
THERE ARE THOUSANDS OF
REGISTERED STATION-WAGON OWNERS

23:23.709 --> 23:25.083
IN MIAMI-DADE COUNTY,

23:25.083 --> 23:27.041
BUT GUESS WHO'S NOT
ON THE LIST?

23:27.041 --> 23:28.667
THE NIGHT WATCHMAN.

23:28.667 --> 23:30.709
I KNEW LaGUERTA HAD HER HEAD
UP HER ASS ON THAT ONE.

23:30.709 --> 23:33.041
SHE DOESN'T HAVE SHIT
ON THE REAL ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

23:33.041 --> 23:34.709
GOOD.

23:34.709 --> 23:36.166
WHY GOOD?

23:38.041 --> 23:39.750
IT'S GOOD FOR YOU.

23:39.750 --> 23:43.417
YOU'RE GONNA BE THE ONE TO
APPREHEND THAT HEINOUS MURDERER,

23:43.417 --> 23:45.875
NOT HER.

23:45.875 --> 23:48.291
THANKS.

23:48.291 --> 23:50.959
ALL RIGHT.
GOOD NIGHT, SISTER.

23:53.333 --> 23:54.959
DON'T STAY UP TOO LATE.

23:54.959 --> 23:56.667
OKAY.

23:56.667 --> 23:59.667
THANKS FOR STOPPING BY.

23:59.667 --> 24:01.208
[ FROGS CROAKING ]

24:06.291 --> 24:08.417
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

24:12.166 --> 24:13.542
HELLO?

24:13.542 --> 24:14.583
Rita: Hi.

24:14.583 --> 24:16.417
Are you --
is this a bad time?

24:16.417 --> 24:17.834
It's Rita.

24:17.834 --> 24:19.417
NO, IT'S FINE.
HI.

24:19.417 --> 24:23.125
I WAS JUST, UH,
READING A SAD STORY.

24:23.125 --> 24:24.458
Is everything okay?

24:24.458 --> 24:26.917
YES, I'M --
LOOK, THE THING IS...

24:26.917 --> 24:29.250
You need me to pick up Cody
after school?

24:29.250 --> 24:30.458
NO.

24:30.458 --> 24:32.959
COLLEEN'S GONNA TAKE HIM
TO KARATE WITH HUDSON.

24:32.959 --> 24:34.709
WHAT ABOUT ASTOR'S PIANO?

24:34.709 --> 24:36.166
Jen's got that covered.

24:36.166 --> 24:38.208
LOOK,
IT'S SOCIAL SERVICES.

24:38.208 --> 24:40.959
THERE'S A CASEWORKER COMING BY
THE HOUSE THIS AFTERNOON.

24:40.959 --> 24:44.250
I SHOULD BE HOME BY 4:00,
BUT WITH THE BUSES...

24:44.250 --> 24:46.166
I'll be there.

24:46.166 --> 24:48.875
Don't worry about a thing.

24:48.875 --> 24:51.291
THANK YOU, DEXTER.

24:51.291 --> 24:53.375
Doakes: AS YOU ALL KNOW,

24:53.375 --> 24:55.917
A NIGHT WATCHMAN FROM
THE HOCKEY ARENA IS MISSING.

24:55.917 --> 24:58.000
TILL NOW, WE PRESUMED
HE WAS ABDUCTED

24:58.000 --> 24:59.959
OR MURDERED
BY THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

24:59.959 --> 25:01.834
HOWEVER, WE SEARCHED
HIS APARTMENT

25:01.834 --> 25:03.792
AND FOUND A STOLEN
SURVEILLANCE TAPE

25:03.792 --> 25:05.750
FROM THE NIGHT OF THE MURDER.

25:05.750 --> 25:08.583
CHIEF OF SECURITY AT
THE HOCKEY ARENA CONFIRMED IT.

25:08.583 --> 25:11.083
THE MAN YOU'RE LOOKING AT
IS TONY TUCCI,

25:11.083 --> 25:12.625
THE MISSING NIGHT WATCHMAN.

25:12.625 --> 25:15.250
AND HERE'S THE BEST PART --
TUCCI HAS A RECORD.

25:15.250 --> 25:17.667
HE PULLED A KNIFE
AT A PARTY IN '97.

25:17.667 --> 25:20.375
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

25:20.375 --> 25:23.208
I GIVE YOU TONY TUCCI,
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

25:23.208 --> 25:24.667
Bullshit.

25:24.667 --> 25:27.291
CAPTAIN MATTHEWS IS COORDINATING
WITH THE FDLE

25:27.291 --> 25:29.875
TO LAUNCH A STATEWIDE MANHUNT
AS SOON AS WE GET CLEARANCES.

25:29.875 --> 25:32.041
DOES HE DRIVE
A STATION WAGON?

25:32.041 --> 25:33.417
EXCUSE ME?

25:33.417 --> 25:35.458
TUCCI -- WHAT KIND OF CAR
DOES HE DRIVE?

25:35.458 --> 25:37.333
THE LAST-KNOWN VICTIM WAS SEEN
GETTING IN A STATION WAGON.

25:37.333 --> 25:39.709
I DON'T RECALL ASKING FOR
ANY QUESTIONS, MISS MORGAN.

25:39.709 --> 25:41.333
NOW, FROM THIS MOMENT ON,

25:41.333 --> 25:43.333
ALL OUR RESOURCES
GO TO FINDING THIS MAN.

25:43.333 --> 25:45.917
YOUR INDIVIDUAL ASSIGNMENTS
WILL BE COMING SHORTLY.

25:45.917 --> 25:47.667
THAT'S ALL FOR NOW.

25:54.208 --> 25:55.625
DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

25:55.625 --> 25:57.542
AFTER BEING SO CAREFUL
FOR SO LONG,

25:57.542 --> 25:59.542
WHY WOULD HE LEAVE
RECORDED EVIDENCE?

25:59.542 --> 26:01.375
OF COURSE I AGREE
WITH MY SISTER,

26:01.375 --> 26:03.667
BUT UNLIKE HER, I'M NOT UPSET.

26:03.667 --> 26:07.166
HE'S STILL OUT THERE,
AND I'M WAITING...

26:07.166 --> 26:08.458
BREATHLESS.

26:08.458 --> 26:11.166
YOU SURE WE CAN'T
GET YOU ANYTHING?

26:11.166 --> 26:12.542
I'M FINE.

26:12.542 --> 26:14.500
RITA'S USUALLY HOME
IN TIME FOR THE KIDS.

26:14.500 --> 26:16.959
I'M JUST BACKUP.
HER BUS MUST BE LATE.

26:16.959 --> 26:19.208
MY FILES SAY MS. BENNETT'S
SUPPOSED TO HAVE

26:19.208 --> 26:20.792
PERSONAL TRANSPORTATION.

26:20.792 --> 26:23.208
OH, YEAH, WELL, SHE DID
AND WILL AGAIN VERY SOON.

26:23.208 --> 26:24.542
PROBABLY NEXT WEEK.

26:24.542 --> 26:26.583
I JUST HAVE TO
MAKE A NOTE OF IT.

26:26.583 --> 26:30.041
SHE'S DOING
AN EXEMPLARY JOB.

26:30.041 --> 26:33.667
I WISH ALL MY HOME VISITS
WERE THIS LOVELY.

26:33.667 --> 26:35.875
SO WHY DO YOU KEEP
COMING AROUND, THEN?

26:35.875 --> 26:39.542
ROUTINE FOLLOW-UP FOR
ALL DOMESTIC-VIOLENCE CASES.

26:39.542 --> 26:41.583
WE NEED TO ENSURE A STABLE
HOME ENVIRONMENT EXISTS.

26:41.583 --> 26:43.083
IT'S A GOOD THING.

26:43.083 --> 26:45.500
THE SYSTEM DOES WORK
FROM TIME TO TIME.

26:45.500 --> 26:48.125
I WAS ACTUALLY TAKEN IN
BY A WONDERFUL FAMILY.

26:48.125 --> 26:49.917
NO ABUSE.

26:49.917 --> 26:52.083
IN FACT,
MY FOSTER FATHER UNDERSTOOD

26:52.083 --> 26:54.458
I HAD SPECIAL NEEDS.

26:54.458 --> 26:56.500
WITHOUT HIM...

26:56.500 --> 26:59.250
YOU'RE LUCKY.

26:59.250 --> 27:00.625
LUCKY.

27:00.625 --> 27:01.959
I'M HERE!

27:01.959 --> 27:04.250
HEY, EVERYONE, I'M HERE.

27:04.250 --> 27:05.750
THANK YOU.

27:05.750 --> 27:08.834
SORRY.
IT'S OKAY.

27:08.834 --> 27:10.625
I AM LUCKY.

27:10.625 --> 27:12.583
WHAT DO I KNOW ABOUT ABUSE?

27:12.583 --> 27:14.625
WITHOUT THE CODE OF HARRY,

27:14.625 --> 27:17.625
I'M SURE I WOULD'VE COMMITTED
A SENSELESS MURDER IN MY YOUTH

27:17.625 --> 27:19.959
JUST TO WATCH THE BLOOD FLOW.

27:19.959 --> 27:22.333
Nurse: JUST TRY
AND KEEP HIM COMFORTABLE.

27:22.333 --> 27:24.583
IT'S ABOUT ALL WE CAN DO
FOR HIM NOW.

27:24.583 --> 27:26.333
[ Crying ]
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

27:26.333 --> 27:28.333
A WEEK AGO, THE DOCTOR SAID
HE WAS GETTING BETTER.

27:28.333 --> 27:29.834
HE IS GETTING BETTER, SWEETIE.

27:29.834 --> 27:33.417
A BODY CANNOT SUFFER
IN SWEET REPOSE.

27:35.125 --> 27:37.417
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

27:37.417 --> 27:39.834
WHAT THE HELL
DOES THAT MEAN?

27:39.834 --> 27:42.500
SHE'S WEIRD.

27:42.500 --> 27:44.458
Harry: LISTEN, YOU TWO...

27:44.458 --> 27:46.917
I'M NOT GOING TO BE AROUND
MUCH LONGER.

27:46.917 --> 27:48.834
DAD, DON'T SAY THAT.

27:48.834 --> 27:50.959
YOU CAN MAKE IT THROUGH THIS
IF YOU FIGHT.

27:53.291 --> 27:55.000
WHEN I'M GONE,

27:55.000 --> 27:59.208
I WON'T BE ABLE TO STOP YOU
FROM BEING WHO YOU ARE.

27:59.208 --> 28:03.041
SOONER OR LATER,

28:03.041 --> 28:05.291
YOU'LL NEED TO DO IT.

28:05.291 --> 28:07.333
DO WHAT?

28:09.291 --> 28:13.750
JUST REMEMBER OUR LESSONS.

28:13.750 --> 28:17.083
WHAT LESSONS?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

28:17.083 --> 28:19.458
I CAN'T MAKE IT
WITHOUT YOU.

28:19.458 --> 28:21.583
YES, YOU CAN.

28:21.583 --> 28:26.041
IF YOU FEEL LIKE
YOU'RE SLIPPING...

28:26.041 --> 28:28.291
LEAN ON YOUR SISTER.

28:28.291 --> 28:31.917
SHE'LL KEEP YOU CONNECTED.

28:31.917 --> 28:35.333
FUCKING FORENSICS REPORT.

28:35.333 --> 28:36.792
WHAT'D THEY FIND?

28:36.792 --> 28:39.083
TUCCI'S HAIR AND FIBER.

28:39.083 --> 28:41.583
OF COURSE TUCCI'S HAIR
AND FIBERS ARE ON THE BODY.

28:41.583 --> 28:44.458
HE'S HAULING HER AROUND
WITH HIS PORK HANDS, ISN'T HE?

28:44.458 --> 28:46.542
ANY WORD
FROM THE CHEM LAB?

28:46.542 --> 28:48.542
SAME AS THE OTHER MURDERS.

28:48.542 --> 28:51.959
THE KILLER USED LIQUID NITROGEN
TO PRESERVE THE TISSUE,

28:51.959 --> 28:53.750
GIVE IT THAT BLEACHED LOOK.

28:53.750 --> 28:57.500
YOU KNOW HOW UNSTABLE
LIQUID NITROGEN IS?

28:57.500 --> 28:59.375
YOU'D HAVE TO BE A LAB RAT

28:59.375 --> 29:01.542
JUST TO MESS AROUND
WITH THAT SHIT.

29:01.542 --> 29:05.417
TUCCI DIDN'T EVEN PASS
HIGH SCHOOL CHEMISTRY.

29:05.417 --> 29:08.208
WATCH CAREFULLY.
RIGHT THERE -- SEE?

29:08.208 --> 29:10.917
RIGHT BEFORE
HE REPOSITIONED THE TORSO.

29:10.917 --> 29:12.291
HE TURNED HIS HEAD.

29:12.291 --> 29:13.709
LIKE SOMEONE'S
GIVING HIM DIRECTIONS.

29:13.709 --> 29:15.667
SOMEONE LIKE
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER

29:15.667 --> 29:17.417
HOLDING A MOTHERFUCKING GUN
TO HIS BACK.

29:17.417 --> 29:19.250
THE KILLER'S
FRAMING TUCCI.

29:19.250 --> 29:21.041
IT LOOKS THAT WAY.

29:21.041 --> 29:23.792
LaGUERTA'S GONNA LOSE HER
SHEEP SHIT WHEN SHE FINDS OUT.

29:23.792 --> 29:26.166
SHE'S GONNA HAVE TO CANCEL
HER PRESS CONFERENCE.

29:26.166 --> 29:28.583
AND YOU KNOW HOW LaGUERTA
LOVES HER PRESS CONFERENCES.

29:28.583 --> 29:30.417
[ CHUCKLES ]

29:30.417 --> 29:32.917
CAN I BORROW THIS TAPE?

30:11.917 --> 30:13.959
BINGO.

30:13.959 --> 30:17.000
I KNOW WHAT HAPPENS NEXT IN
THIS GRUESOME LITTLE SCENARIO.

30:17.000 --> 30:19.583
JEREMY IS TRYING TO RE-CREATE
HIS FIRST KILL,

30:19.583 --> 30:22.083
RITUALIZE IT.

30:24.333 --> 30:26.458
YOU READY?

30:26.458 --> 30:28.375
I DON'T KNOW
IF I WANT TO DO THIS, MAN.

30:28.375 --> 30:29.709
WHAT'S WRONG?

30:29.709 --> 30:31.375
I THOUGHT YOU WANTED
TO SEE AN ALLIGATOR.

30:31.375 --> 30:32.667
I DO.

30:32.667 --> 30:34.500
IT'S IN THE MARSH UP HERE.

30:34.500 --> 30:37.291
WAIT.
ARE YOU A PUSSY?

30:37.291 --> 30:39.417
NO.

30:39.417 --> 30:40.875
OKAY.

30:45.709 --> 30:48.333
WHERE IS THIS PLACE, MAN?

30:48.333 --> 30:50.458
[ SIGHS ]

30:50.458 --> 30:52.834
IT'S RIGHT UP HERE.

30:52.834 --> 30:54.709
COME ON, JER.

30:54.709 --> 30:56.667
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

30:56.667 --> 30:59.041
DON'T BE A BITCH.

31:01.291 --> 31:03.625
HERE WE ARE.

31:03.625 --> 31:05.834
I DON'T SEE IT.

31:05.834 --> 31:07.667
IT'S RIGHT THERE.

31:07.667 --> 31:09.667
SEE ITS EYES STICKING OUT?

31:14.417 --> 31:16.500
YOU HAVE TO GET CLOSER.

31:19.208 --> 31:22.291
I STILL DON'T SEE IT.

31:22.291 --> 31:25.625
REALLY?

31:25.625 --> 31:28.333
HUH. MAYBE I WAS WRONG.

31:31.792 --> 31:34.333
THERE'S NO GATOR HERE,
IS THERE?

31:37.542 --> 31:39.583
I DON'T KNOW, LUCAS.

31:39.583 --> 31:42.041
IS THERE?

31:43.875 --> 31:46.542
ANYONE SEE A FRISBEE?
IT FLEW IN HERE SOMEWHERE.

32:03.583 --> 32:06.041
WHAT AM I DOING OUT HERE?

32:08.250 --> 32:10.041
[ GROWLS ]

32:10.917 --> 32:13.208
OH, FUCK! FUCK!

32:16.291 --> 32:17.875
FUCK!

32:24.250 --> 32:25.583
[ SPITS ]

32:26.917 --> 32:31.291
ALL I HAD TO DO WAS DRIVE HOME,
HAVE A TACO, PLAN MY ATTACK.

32:31.291 --> 32:34.250
INSTEAD, DEARLY DELUDED DEXTER
TRIED TO ACT HUMAN,

32:34.250 --> 32:36.291
LIKE IT'S MY JOB
TO SAVE LIVES.

32:51.458 --> 32:55.041
CODE OF HARRY
NEVER COVERED THIS.

32:55.041 --> 32:57.792
AT LEAST I KNOW
WHERE JEREMY IS

32:57.792 --> 32:59.917
AND WHAT I NEED TO DO.

33:03.125 --> 33:05.083
Harry: Don't let her.

33:07.291 --> 33:09.625
OKAY,
MY BRAVE LITTLE SOLDIER.

33:09.625 --> 33:12.125
LET'S GET THIS NASTY SHOT
OUT OF THE WAY.

33:12.125 --> 33:14.291
NO! WAIT!

33:14.291 --> 33:15.625
WHAT IS IT, HONEY?

33:15.625 --> 33:17.458
HE DOESN'T WANT THE SHOT.

33:17.458 --> 33:20.000
YOUR FATHER'S VERY SICK.
HE'S IN A LOT OF PAIN.

33:20.000 --> 33:21.458
HE NEEDS A SHOT.

33:21.458 --> 33:23.667
I WANT PAIN.
HE WANTS PAIN.

33:30.959 --> 33:33.625
I'LL HAVE TO TELL
THE DOCTOR.

33:33.625 --> 33:37.792
HE'S NOT GOING TO BE HAPPY
YOU'RE REFUSING YOUR MEDICATION.

33:45.166 --> 33:46.667
Harry: YOU CAN TELL.

33:46.667 --> 33:48.667
ABOUT THE NURSE?
YEAH.

33:48.667 --> 33:53.166
SHE'S...LIKE ME.

33:54.792 --> 33:57.542
HOW COULD YOU TELL?

33:57.542 --> 34:02.417
SHE GIVES TOO MUCH...
MORPHINE.

34:02.417 --> 34:05.375
IT'S SOMETHING ELSE.

34:05.375 --> 34:07.000
IT'S MAKING ME WORSE.

34:07.000 --> 34:09.000
SHE'S DRUGGING YOU.

34:09.000 --> 34:11.333
SHE'S KILLING YOU
BY OVERDOSE.

34:11.333 --> 34:14.041
NOT JUST ME.
OTHERS, TOO.

34:25.542 --> 34:28.375
Stop her.

34:28.375 --> 34:32.208
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
STOP HER?

34:32.208 --> 34:35.083
IT'S TIME.

34:35.083 --> 34:39.208
BEFORE SHE HURTS
ANYONE ELSE.

34:43.125 --> 34:45.917
Debra: SEE THE LOOK ON HIS FACE,
LIKE HE'S SCARED?

34:45.917 --> 34:48.625
LIKE HE HAS A GUN
POINTED AT HIM?

34:48.625 --> 34:51.083
OH, I DON'T KNOW, DEBRA.

34:51.083 --> 34:53.583
IT'S NOT MUCH --
A LOOK OFF-CAMERA.

34:53.583 --> 34:54.875
THERE'S MORE.

34:54.875 --> 34:57.083
ONE OF MY VICE CONTACTS,
GABRIELLE -- I TRUST HER --

34:57.083 --> 34:58.917
SHE SAW THE VICTIM
GET INTO A WOOD-PANELED WAGON

34:58.917 --> 35:00.959
THE NIGHT
OF THE VICTIM'S DEATH.

35:00.959 --> 35:02.792
THAT WAS THE LAST TIME
ANYONE SAW HER.

35:02.792 --> 35:04.709
DID A BACKGROUND REPORT
ON TUCCI.

35:04.709 --> 35:06.709
HE DOESN'T EVEN OWN A CAR.

35:06.709 --> 35:09.667
THERE'S NO FUCKING WAY THIS GUY
CAN BE THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

35:09.667 --> 35:11.709
SIR.

35:11.709 --> 35:14.542
WHAT DOES LIEUTENANT LaGUERTA
SAY ABOUT ALL THIS?

35:14.542 --> 35:16.875
I CAME STRAIGHT TO YOU,
CAPTAIN.

35:16.875 --> 35:19.291
YOU WENT AROUND THE BACK
OF YOUR COMMANDING OFFICER?

35:19.291 --> 35:21.250
LaGUERTA
DOESN'T LISTEN TO ME.

35:21.250 --> 35:24.125
YOU DON'T VIOLATE
THE CHAIN OF COMMAND.

35:24.125 --> 35:25.917
YOU JUST DON'T.

35:25.917 --> 35:27.291
NOW, LISTEN, DEBRA.

35:27.291 --> 35:29.458
I GAVE YOU A SHOT
IN HOMICIDE

35:29.458 --> 35:31.834
BECAUSE I THINK YOU CAN MAKE
A HALFWAY-DECENT DETECTIVE.

35:31.834 --> 35:34.458
BUT IF I FIND YOU CAN'T
SWIM IN THESE WATERS,

35:34.458 --> 35:36.500
I'LL PUT YOU
RIGHT BACK ON THE STREET.

35:36.500 --> 35:38.125
YOU GOT IT?

35:38.125 --> 35:40.333
YES, SIR.

35:40.333 --> 35:42.667
YOUR FATHER
NEVER WOULD'VE PULLED

35:42.667 --> 35:44.250
THE KIND OF SHIT
YOU JUST DID.

35:48.500 --> 35:51.625
DID YOU KNOW THAT ONE
OF YOUR OFFICERS HAS INFORMATION

35:51.625 --> 35:54.458
THAT CASTS SOME DOUBT
ON THIS MANHUNT OF YOURS?

35:54.458 --> 35:56.709
WHO, MORGAN?

35:56.709 --> 36:00.917
I REALIZE YOU'RE SOMETHING OF
A FOLK HERO AROUND HERE, MARIA,

36:00.917 --> 36:02.542
BUT IT WOULD BE A MISTAKE

36:02.542 --> 36:04.834
TO IGNORE THE WORK
OF A PROMISING OFFICER

36:04.834 --> 36:07.041
JUST TO FURTHER
YOUR POLITICAL CAREER.

36:07.041 --> 36:08.625
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK
I'M DOING?

36:08.625 --> 36:10.500
YOU WERE A MIDDLE-OF-THE-PACK
DETECTIVE

36:10.500 --> 36:12.041
BEFORE THE PRESS
GOT AHOLD OF YOU.

36:12.041 --> 36:14.041
THANKS FOR THE VOTE
OF CONFIDENCE.

36:14.041 --> 36:16.000
IT'S A REALITY CHECK,
AND YOU NEED IT.

36:16.000 --> 36:19.417
AND I GOT IT.

36:19.417 --> 36:21.333
LET'S CUT TO THE CHASE.

36:21.333 --> 36:23.834
ARE YOU TELLING ME
TO CALL OFF MY MANHUNT?

36:23.834 --> 36:25.333
'CAUSE I WILL REMIND YOU

36:25.333 --> 36:27.166
THAT JEB BUSH HIMSELF
SIGNED OFF ON IT.

36:27.166 --> 36:28.792
NO, UH, NO.

36:28.792 --> 36:31.417
YOU GO AHEAD AND HOLD
YOUR PRESS CONFERENCE, MARIA.

36:31.417 --> 36:33.250
PEOPLE OF THIS CITY
NEED TO KNOW

36:33.250 --> 36:35.166
WE'RE DOING SOMETHING
ABOUT THIS MESS.

36:35.166 --> 36:37.417
BUT DON'T EXPECT ME
TO BAIL YOU OUT

36:37.417 --> 36:41.417
IF THAT NIGHT WATCHMAN
TURNS OUT TO BE A DEAD END.

36:41.417 --> 36:44.500
A STATEWIDE MANHUNT IS UNDER
WAY RIGHT NOW IN FLORIDA.

36:44.500 --> 36:47.166
ACCORDING TO POLICE,
A NIGHT WATCHMAN IS ON THE RUN

36:47.166 --> 36:49.458
AFTER THE DISMEMBERED
BODY PARTS

36:49.458 --> 36:51.875
OF A YOUNG SOUTH BEACH WOMAN
WERE FOUND TUESDAY,

36:51.875 --> 36:54.333
STACKED ON THE HOME ICE
OF THE MIAMI BLADES.

36:54.333 --> 36:56.834
THE WOMAN IS BELIEVED
TO BE THE LATEST VICTIM

36:56.834 --> 36:59.000
OF THE NOTORIOUS
ICE-TRUCK KILLER,

36:59.000 --> 37:03.125
NOW RESPONSIBLE FOR FIVE DEATHS
IN THE GREATER MIAMI AREA.

37:03.125 --> 37:05.875
THESE TERRIBLE ATTACKS
HAVE TO STOP.

37:05.875 --> 37:07.667
AND WE HAVE TO STOP THEM.

37:07.667 --> 37:11.041
WITH TONY TUCCI
NOW LINKED TO THE MURDERS,

37:11.041 --> 37:12.750
IT'S OUR MISSION TO FIND HIM.

37:12.750 --> 37:15.875
FUCKING JOKE.

37:15.875 --> 37:17.834
HEY, GOING OUT TONIGHT
WITH THE GUYS,

37:17.834 --> 37:19.792
BLOW OFF A LITTLE STEAM --
YOU IN?

37:19.792 --> 37:21.041
HEY, MAN, SOUNDS GOOD.

37:21.041 --> 37:23.250
PICK YOU UP AT 8:00.

37:29.667 --> 37:32.208
ELEVATOR'S AROUND THE CORNER
AND TO YOUR LEFT.

37:32.208 --> 37:34.417
ENJOY YOUR STAY WITH US.

37:38.917 --> 37:40.792
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

37:44.583 --> 37:46.166
HELLO?

37:46.166 --> 37:48.250
Rita, this is Mr. Curtis.

37:48.250 --> 37:50.291
Are you coming
to pick up Astor?

37:50.291 --> 37:53.917
OH, NO, A FRIEND OF MINE IS --
DENISE.

37:53.917 --> 37:55.458
IS SHE NOT THERE?

37:55.458 --> 37:58.125
I'm afraid not,
but your daughter is.

37:58.125 --> 38:01.333
She's the last kid left
here at school.

38:01.333 --> 38:04.792
I DON'T HAVE A CAR.
IS SHE OKAY?

38:04.792 --> 38:06.417
Yeah, she's just fine,

38:06.417 --> 38:09.458
but we can't keep her here
much longer.

38:09.458 --> 38:11.583
OKAY.

38:11.583 --> 38:14.125
OKAY,
I'LL WORK SOMETHING OUT.

38:16.166 --> 38:18.291
[ LAUGHING ]

38:23.750 --> 38:25.166
PHEW!

38:25.166 --> 38:26.625
DO IT AGAIN!

38:26.625 --> 38:28.375
Shh.
LET'S NOT WAKE UP CODY.

38:28.375 --> 38:31.333
NOW, LET'S SEE
ABOUT THAT SPLINTER.

38:33.625 --> 38:34.792
OOH.

38:34.792 --> 38:36.709
THAT'S A DEEP ONE.

38:36.709 --> 38:38.709
THIS MIGHT STING A BIT.

38:38.709 --> 38:40.959
BUT THE MAGICAL
SPLINTER FAIRY

38:40.959 --> 38:43.291
WILL SOON MAKE YOU
FORGET ALL ABOUT IT.

38:43.291 --> 38:45.041
WHO'S THE MAGICAL
SPLINTER FAIRY?

38:45.041 --> 38:47.458
SHE'S THE SECOND COUSIN
TO THE TOOTH FAIRY.

38:47.458 --> 38:48.959
SHE BRINGS CANDY

38:48.959 --> 38:51.750
IF YOU PUT YOUR SPLINTER
UNDER YOUR PILLOW AT NIGHT.

38:51.750 --> 38:54.625
THE TOOTH FAIRY IS MAKE-BELIEVE,
JUST LIKE THE BOOGEYMAN.

38:56.166 --> 38:57.500
Rita: HI, GUYS.

38:57.500 --> 38:58.500
OW!

38:58.500 --> 39:00.041
OOH! YOU'RE RIGHT, ASTOR.

39:00.041 --> 39:02.125
THERE'S SO SUCH THING
AS THE BOOGEYMAN.

39:02.125 --> 39:04.625
BUT THE SPLINTER FAIRY --
SHE'S THE REAL DEAL.

39:04.625 --> 39:08.625
WILL THE SPLINTER FAIRY COME
IF I CRY?

39:12.333 --> 39:17.959
THANKS FOR PICKING HER UP.

39:19.625 --> 39:21.667
IF I HAD A HEART,
IT M  [ SPANISH MUSIC PLAYS
]OW.

39:30.375 --> 39:32.333
[ HORNS HONKING ]

39:57.542 --> 39:59.542
[ HORN HONKS, BRAKES SQUEAL ]

40:20.542 --> 40:22.542
[ BIRD SQUAWKING ]

40:50.125 --> 40:51.750
WHO WE PICKING UP NOW, MAN?

40:51.750 --> 40:53.792
'CAUSE HE SURE AIN'T
SITTING ON MY LAP.

40:53.792 --> 40:56.709
Mac: WE'RE NOT PICKING UP
ANYBODY, BRO.

40:56.709 --> 40:58.875
WELL, WHAT WE DOING
IN THE GABLES?

40:58.875 --> 41:02.959
I TOLD YOU.
WE'RE BLOWING OFF SOME STEAM.

41:02.959 --> 41:04.959
THIS IS IT.

41:04.959 --> 41:06.709
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

41:06.709 --> 41:09.125
IT'S A DISGUISE.

41:09.125 --> 41:11.291
ONE OF GUERRERO'S
TOP LIEUTENANTS --

41:11.291 --> 41:13.625
HE LIVES HERE,
AND WE'RE GONNA FUCK HIM UP.

41:13.625 --> 41:14.792
HOLD UP, MAC.

41:14.792 --> 41:16.333
I THOUGHT YOU SAID

41:16.333 --> 41:18.709
YOU WANTED TO GO OUT
AND GET SHIT-FACED, MAN.

41:18.709 --> 41:21.875
I AM SHIT-FACED.

41:21.875 --> 41:23.500
HOW DO I LOOK?

41:23.500 --> 41:25.834
[ LAUGHS ]

41:25.834 --> 41:28.291
MAN, I'M ALL FOR
SENDING THE MESSAGE,

41:28.291 --> 41:30.125
BUT THIS --
THIS AIN'T THE WAY, MAN.

41:30.125 --> 41:31.792
WHY THE HELL NOT?

41:31.792 --> 41:33.959
THE GUY'S SCUM.

41:40.125 --> 41:42.792
MAC, LISTEN.
I'VE GOT TO TALK TO YOU.

41:42.792 --> 41:44.166
MAC, MAC!

41:44.166 --> 41:46.166
HEY, LISTEN UP, MAN.

41:46.166 --> 41:48.458
I SHOWED MY FACE
TO GUERRERO.

41:48.458 --> 41:50.917
THEY GONNA THINK
I'M BEHIND THIS SHIT.

41:50.917 --> 41:52.375
THAT'S PART OF THE PLAN.

41:52.375 --> 41:53.709
WHAT PLAN?

41:53.709 --> 41:56.333
YOU FUCKED MY SISTER.
YOU FUCKED A COP'S WIFE.

41:56.333 --> 41:58.583
NOW YOU'RE JUST FUCKED, BUDDY.

41:58.583 --> 41:59.750
WHOO!

41:59.750 --> 42:01.500
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

42:06.667 --> 42:08.625
[ GLASS SHATTERING ]

42:08.625 --> 42:11.667
[ MUFFLED SHOUTING ]

42:11.667 --> 42:13.000
Shit.

42:14.166 --> 42:16.667
MOTHERFUCKER!

42:20.875 --> 42:22.625
Fuck.

42:24.875 --> 42:27.500
[ VIDEO GAME BEEPING ]

42:44.917 --> 42:47.542
HEY, QUIT FUCKING AROUND.
TURN ON THE LIGHTS.

42:49.542 --> 42:52.417
COME ON, MAN.
TURN ON THE FUCKING LIGHTS!

42:54.542 --> 42:55.542
AAH!

42:57.417 --> 42:58.875
YOU'RE MINE NOW.

42:58.875 --> 43:00.750
WHAT DO YOU WANT?
SILENCE.

43:00.750 --> 43:02.333
YOU GONNA FUCK ME, FAGGOT?

43:02.333 --> 43:05.375
'CAUSE I KILLED THE LAST GUY
WHO RAPED ME.

43:05.375 --> 43:07.875
WHAT GUY?

43:11.458 --> 43:13.834
HE RAPED YOU...

43:13.834 --> 43:16.208
THE GUY YOU KILLED
WHEN YOU WERE 15?

43:17.542 --> 43:20.041
WHY DIDN'T YOU
TELL ANYBODY?

43:20.041 --> 43:22.250
WOULD YOU?

43:24.291 --> 43:26.667
HE FUCKED ME,
AND I KILLED HIM,

43:26.667 --> 43:29.792
AND IF YOU TRY,
I'LL KILL YOU, TOO.

43:29.792 --> 43:31.750
I UNDERSTAND NOW.

43:31.750 --> 43:33.625
WHY DIDN'T I SEE IT BEFORE?

43:33.625 --> 43:37.125
JEREMY DIDN'T MURDER THAT BOY
FOUR YEARS AGO.

43:37.125 --> 43:39.250
HE WAS TAKING OUT THE GARBAGE.

43:39.250 --> 43:41.709
JUST LIKE I DO.

43:45.417 --> 43:47.709
LOOK, I REALLY DON'T WANT
TO CANCEL ALL MY CREDIT CARDS,

43:47.709 --> 43:49.875
AND I HATE WAITING IN LINE
AT THE DMV,

43:49.875 --> 43:52.041
SO GIVE ME BACK THE WALLET
YOU STOLE FROM MY CAR,

43:52.041 --> 43:54.083
OR I'LL BREAK
YOUR FUCKING NECK.

43:56.375 --> 43:58.125
IT'S IN MY BACKPACK.

44:15.625 --> 44:17.792
WAIT -- IS THAT ALL?

44:20.709 --> 44:22.417
YOU WANT MORE?

44:27.208 --> 44:29.834
THAT BOY WHO RAPED YOU
FOUR YEARS AGO --

44:29.834 --> 44:31.583
DID HE DESERVE TO DIE?

44:31.583 --> 44:34.583
YEAH.

44:34.583 --> 44:36.291
HE DID.

44:36.291 --> 44:38.542
WELL, THE BOY LAST NIGHT DIDN'T.

44:40.834 --> 44:43.875
REMEMBER THAT.
IT COULD SAVE YOUR LIFE ONE DAY.

44:55.834 --> 44:58.583
MR. TINKER?

44:58.583 --> 45:00.083
[ CAT MEOWS ]

45:00.083 --> 45:02.834
MR. TINKER, WHERE ARE YOU?

45:04.667 --> 45:06.291
MR. TINKER?

45:08.125 --> 45:10.333
ARE YOU TRAPPED
BEHIND THE COUCH AGAIN,

45:10.333 --> 45:13.458
MR. TINKER-STINKER?

45:13.458 --> 45:16.208
THE NURSE
WAS MY FIRST PLAYMATE.

45:16.208 --> 45:17.917
I'LL ALWAYS BE GRATEFUL TO HER

45:17.917 --> 45:21.333
FOR OPENING UP SO MANY
MAGNIFICENT NEW DOORS FOR ME.

45:38.917 --> 45:41.834
THINGS WERE A LITTLE MESSY
IN THE BEGINNING.

45:41.834 --> 45:45.542
HEY, PERFECTING A NEW CRAFT
TAKES TIME.

45:45.542 --> 45:47.333
BUT I WAS TRAINED WELL.

45:47.333 --> 45:49.875
THOSE WHO WITNESSED
MY EARLY STUMBLES

45:49.875 --> 45:51.834
NEVER HAD A CHANCE TO TELL.

46:03.750 --> 46:05.709
[ GASPS ]

46:09.250 --> 46:13.375
I'VE JUST BEEN LOOKING
THROUGH YOUR PHOTO ALBUM.

46:13.375 --> 46:15.458
HOPE YOU DON'T MIND.

46:18.125 --> 46:20.875
ARE ALL YOUR VICTIMS IN HERE?

46:38.458 --> 46:40.458
[ MUFFLED GRUNTS ]

46:40.458 --> 46:43.166
I'M SORRY.
LET ME HELP YOU WITH THAT.

46:48.375 --> 46:49.583
[ MUFFLED SCREAM ]

46:49.583 --> 46:51.750
SCREAM AND LOSE A TONGUE.

46:58.291 --> 47:01.000
[ GASPS ]

47:01.000 --> 47:02.750
[ COUGHS ]

47:07.458 --> 47:10.458
I-I HELPED THEM...

47:10.458 --> 47:13.333
ALL OF THEM.

47:15.291 --> 47:18.834
I TOOK THEIR PAIN AWAY.

47:18.834 --> 47:20.625
I UNDERSTAND.

47:22.875 --> 47:25.500
NOW IT'S TIME
TO TAKE AWAY YOUR PAIN.

47:39.542 --> 47:42.083
IT WAS MESSIER
THAN I ANTICIPATED,

47:42.083 --> 47:44.792
BUT IT WAS STILL A SPECIAL DAY.

47:49.166 --> 47:51.667
BUT, OF COURSE,
IT WAS REALLY HARRY

47:51.667 --> 47:54.458
WHO PAVED THE ROAD
TO MY SALVATION.

47:57.083 --> 47:59.000
WITH THE NURSE PUT DOWN,

47:59.000 --> 48:01.208
HARRY LIVED ANOTHER YEAR
BEFORE HARDENING ARTERIES

48:01.208 --> 48:04.959
SQUEEZED THE LAST BIT
OF LIFE FROM HIM,

48:04.959 --> 48:07.375
BUT HIS LESSONS
HAVE NEVER FAILED ME.

48:12.041 --> 48:15.542
HARRY TAUGHT ME
THAT DEATH ISN'T THE END.

48:15.542 --> 48:17.917
IT'S THE BEGINNING
OF A CHAIN REACTION

48:17.917 --> 48:21.375
THAT WILL CATCH YOU
IF YOU'RE NOT CAREFUL.

48:29.542 --> 48:31.417
HE TAUGHT ME THAT NONE OF US

48:31.417 --> 48:34.000
ARE WHO WE APPEAR TO BE
ON THE OUTSIDE...

48:37.166 --> 48:40.458
...BUT WE MUST MAINTAIN
APPEARANCES TO SURVIVE.

48:49.875 --> 48:52.417
BUT THERE WAS SOMETHING
HARRY DIDN'T TEACH ME,

48:52.417 --> 48:56.000
SOMETHING HE DIDN'T KNOW,
COULDN'T POSSIBLY KNOW.

48:56.000 --> 48:57.834
THE WILLFUL TAKING OF LIFE

48:57.834 --> 49:00.917
REPRESENTS THE ULTIMATE
DISCONNECT FROM HUMANITY.

49:00.917 --> 49:03.959
IT LEAVES YOU AN OUTSIDER,
FOREVER LOOKING IN,

49:03.959 --> 49:06.750
SEARCHING FOR COMPANY TO KEEP.

49:06.750 --> 49:08.542
[ CAR HORN HONKS ]

49:17.750 --> 49:19.458
SWEET RIDE!

49:19.458 --> 49:21.208
IS IT YOURS?

49:21.208 --> 49:24.709
IT'S YOURS, UNTIL YOUR MOM
CAN GET A NEW ONE.

49:24.709 --> 49:27.417
I BORROWED IT FROM IMPOUND
RIGHT BEFORE AUCTION.

49:27.417 --> 49:29.375
DEXTER...
CAN WE GET IN?

49:29.375 --> 49:30.750
YOU BETTER.

49:35.250 --> 49:37.792
ALL YOU CAN DO
IS PLAY ALONG AT LIFE

49:37.792 --> 49:39.583
AND HOPE THAT SOMETIMES
YOU GET IT RIGHT.

49:46.500 --> 49:48.625
THANK YOU.

49:59.709 --> 50:02.917
SCORE ONE
FOR THE LITTLE WOODEN BOY.

